---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ContactForm from "../components/ContactForm.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Contacto | Marea Creativa Agencia Digital"
  description="Ponte en contacto con Marea Creativa. Hablemos sobre tu próximo proyecto de diseño web, SEO o inteligencia artificial y veamos cómo podemos ayudarte."
  keywords="contacto marea creativa, agencia seo alicante, diseño web contacto, presupuesto diseño web, consultoria marketing digital"
  image="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgkdq8kzk/image/upload/v1771944145/home_hero_yqmogi.png"
>
  <!-- Main Top Section (Hero + Form) -->
  <section
    class="w-full bg-white pt-6 md:pt-10 pb-10 px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="max-w-5xl lg:max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <ContactForm />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section (Bottom, Full Width Grid) -->
  <section class="py-10 md:py-14 bg-[#f8f9fb] border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl lg:max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-8 text-center md:text-left fade-in-up">
        <h2
          class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-3"
        >
          Preguntas Frecuentes
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base max-w-2xl">
          Resolvemos las dudas habituales acerca de nuestras soluciones
          digitales.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 fade-in-up"
        style="animation-delay: 100ms;"
      >
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <details
          class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-5 md:p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all cursor-pointer overflow-hidden open:pb-6"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-gray-900 list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div
                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="16"
                  height="16"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z"></path><path
                    d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path><path
                    d="M12 17h.01"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>¿Qué incluye el Diseño Web?</span>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-blue-600 font-medium text-2xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300 origin-center"
              >+</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-11 animate-fade-in-down"
          >
            Nuestros proyectos incluyen diseño a medida responsive,
            configuración del entorno web y optimización SEO on-page básica.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <details
          class="group bg-white rounded-[24px] border border-gray-100 p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all cursor-pointer overflow-hidden open:pb-8"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-900 list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="20"
                  height="20"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z"></path><path
                    d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path><path
                    d="M12 17h.01"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>¿Cómo funcionan los Chatbots de IA?</span>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-blue-600 font-medium text-2xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300 origin-center"
              >+</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-11 animate-fade-in-down"
          >
            Entrenamos a una IA con los datos de tu empresa. Atiende a clientes
            24/7 en tu web o WhatsApp, respondiendo dudas y captando leads por
            ti.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <details
          class="group bg-white rounded-[24px] border border-gray-100 p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all cursor-pointer overflow-hidden open:pb-8"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-900 list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="20"
                  height="20"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z"></path><path
                    d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path><path
                    d="M12 17h.01"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>¿Cómo mejoran mi Google Business?</span>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-blue-600 font-medium text-2xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300 origin-center"
              >+</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-11 animate-fade-in-down"
          >
            Optimizamos tu Perfil de Empresa y automatizamos la captación de
            reseñas de tus mejores clientes para mejorar tu SEO local.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <details
          class="group bg-white rounded-[24px] border border-gray-100 p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all cursor-pointer overflow-hidden open:pb-8"
        >
          <summary
            class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-900 list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
          >
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="20"
                  height="20"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z"></path><path
                    d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path><path
                    d="M12 17h.01"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>¿Para qué industrias trabajan?</span>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-blue-600 font-medium text-2xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300 origin-center"
              >+</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-11 animate-fade-in-down"
          >
            Trabajamos con diversos sectores: hostelería, clínicas,
            inmobiliarias, e-commerce, y empresas de servicios B2B. Adaptamos
            nuestra metodología a cada nicho.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .fade-in-up {
    animation: fadeInUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
